What you’ll now get from /mcp/attachment_checker_mcp

✅ Success (attachments present)

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "result": {
    "status": true,
    "attachments": [
      { "filename": "file.pdf", "is_duplicate": false }
    ]
  }
}

✅ Success (Gmail empty or no attachments)

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "result": {
    "status": true,
    "attachments": []
  }
}

❌ Failure (Azure/Gmail exception, missing .env, etc.)

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "result": {
    "status": false,
    "error": "Missing AZURE_STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING"
  }
}

